Description: Clients for the Schooltool common platform for school administration
 SchoolTool is a project to develop a common global school administration
 infrastructure that is freely available under an Open Source licence.
 .
 This package contains the the architecture independent parts of the
 SchoolTool clients (GUI and command line).
 .
 Homepage: http://www.schooltool.org/

Package: libschooltool
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Common architecture dependent files for the SchoolTool and SchoolBell server
 SchoolTool is a project to develop a common global school administration
 infrastructure that is freely available under an Open Source licence.
 .
 This package contains all of the architecture dependent parts of SchoolTool
 server.
 .
 Homepage: http://www.schooltool.org

Package: libschooltool-clients
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
